Class FarmerType

java.lang.Object
FarmerType
Direct Known Subclasses:
DistinguishedFarmer, Farmer, LegendaryFarmer, RegisteredFarmer
public abstract class FarmerType extends Object
This is the abstract FarmerType class for the farming simulator game for MCO2.

Methods mostly include getting information on the respective farmer type, including name, level requirement, bonus earnings, seed cost reduction, water bonus increase, fertilizer bonus incrase, and registration fee.
